2011-01-24|2011-01-30.description: Did you hear? Deadpool‘s done, outta the merc game. But there’s a new player in town, and this cat is baaaad. He’s got crazy space-guns, an intergalactic hooptie, and a rep that’s getting bigger by the day and just about the coolest name ever. And he’s here on earth to let everybody know…starting with Deadpool!
2011-01-24|2011-01-30.name: Badass

2011-02-21|2011-02-27.description:
This one’s got it all! The return of Doctor Octopus, Daredevil, a wedding you never predicted, and the return of one of the most important people in Peter Parker’s life. Doc’s back in town, but it’s only a prelude to darker days ahead as Spidey unknowingly prepares for a gauntlet he can’t even see coming!!!

Also, while the machinations of Norman Osborn’s Dark Reign have our favourite heroes on the run, what’s life like for the everyday folks of the Marvel Universe? See how the Amazing Spider-Man changed one man’s life – and how this new world order can undo that good in an instant!

Includes material reprinted from Amazing Spider-Man #600 and Amazing Spider-Man Family #10!

2011-04-04|2011-04-10.description:
In chapter two of the three-part epic "The Darkest Horse," the team finds out the terrible conditions required to use a "Get Out of Hell Free" card that allows them to retrieve the body and soul of a fallen loved one! But who has the card, and who do they want to bring back from Hell itself?

The Secret Six finds themselves in Hell facing Ragdoll's army of the Secret Six-Hundred and Sixty Six. After a brief battle the Secret Six are beaten and it is revealed that Knockout is Ragdoll's princess in Hell.

Meanwhile, Catman and The Demon have left the group on a mission to find Catman's father.
2011-04-04|2011-04-10.name: The Darkest House, Part Two of Three

2011-04-18|2011-04-24.description: The Red Hulk has nowhere to call home. He can't sleep or he'll run the risk of turning human…to be killed immediately by the formidable General Fortean. The Red Hulk needs time and answers; instead he gets another unstoppable hunter created by Zero/One just for him!
2011-04-18|2011-04-24.name: The Rising Fog; Hulk Homework

2011-07-04|2011-07-10.description: "The Draong King's Daughter." Ebony's cravings lead him into a world undreamed of, where he journeys dark-eyed, axe in hand, and becomes a prince among thieves, a ruthless mercenary and a slaughterer of demons, and yet also a prisoner of his own melancholy and a love that can never be returned!
2011-07-04|2011-07-10.name: Man & Elephantman Part 3, The Dragonking's Daughter; The Power of the Elephant

2011-07-11|2011-07-17.description: Surrounded by the Nazi war machine, Captain Armitage must lead his troops against the unholy terror that lurks off the shores of Dunkirk in order to save the King's army from utter destruction.

2011-11-14|2011-11-20.description: HorrorHound covers horror news from the San Diego Comic-Con, including the latest on Dark Shadows, Underworld: Awakening, Ghost Rider, Total Recall, Abraham Lincoln: Vampire Hunter, and the upcoming Alien prequel! Plus, the latest toy news from NECA, Sideshow Collectibles, Mattel, and Hot Toys. All of our regular features including Video Invasion, Horror's Hallowed Grounds, Fantasm, Collect This! and a surprise Horror Retrospective are also included.

DARKNESS APPROACHES

His battle with Fate looms ever closer, but Negi has more pressing concerns. The darkness has started to consume him, and if he doesn't get it under control, he'll turn into a monster. Before Negi can keep his students safe from Fate, he has to keep them safe from himself.

This volume of Negima! includes special extras after the story!
